  <div class="whyus-section text-center mt-5">
    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <div class="why-us-cards d-flex mt-4 container">
      <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center mx-0">
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="why-us-card">
            <img src="/images/local.webp" alt="">
            <h3>Your local company</h3>
            <p>Established in 2016, Pawlett Plumbing & Heating Ltd are a local family-run business operating throughout Aberdeenshire and surrounding areas. We pride ourselves on offering our customers a high quality, friendly and reliable service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="why-us-card">
            <img src="/images/rates.webp" alt="">
            <h3>Fair and Local Rates</h3>
            <p>We charge local rates to North East of Scotland. Fair and transparent pricing, ask for a detailed fixed-price quotation today.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="why-us-card">
            <img src="/images/experts.webp" alt="">
            <h3>Experts</h3>
            <p>With over 12 years experience in the field all engineers at PPH are  fully qualified and insured Gas Safe registered engineers. All of our workforce are trained through a 4 year modern apprenticeship programme giving us the skills to install and maintain hot and cold water, gas central heating, drainage and weathering systems in all commercial, industrial and residential buildings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="services-section text-center mt-5">
    <h2 id="Services">Our Services</h2>
    <div class="service-cards d-flex mt-4 container">
      <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="service-card">
            <img src="/images/plumbing.webp" alt="">
            <h3>Plumbing</h3>
            <ul class="list-group mt-5">
              <li class="list-group-item">Emergency plumbing repairs</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Vented & Unvented hot water systems</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Leak trace and repair </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">General domestic and commercial plumbing maintenance </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Outside tap installations and repair.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Drainage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="service-card">
            <img src="/images/boilers.webp" alt="">
            <h3>Boilers, Central Heating & Gas Services</h3>
            <ul class="list-group">
              <li class="list-group-item"> Gas boiler annual servicing</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Central heating boiler installation and repair</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Landlords gas safety inspections and certification</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Underfloor heating </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Radiator replacement </li>
              <li class="list-group-item">Central heating power flushes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-4">
          <div class="service-card">
            <img src="/images/bathroom2.png" alt="" id="bathroom-img">
            <h3>Bathrooms</h3>
            <p class="mt-5" id="bathrooms-description">We provide a bespoke bathroom design and installation service. We project manage the job working alongside local quality subcontractors. All of the Plumbing, Joinery, Tiling, Plastering, Electrical and Decoration works needed are taken care of so you don’t have to source individual tradesmen yourself. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/">Learn more about our services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="aboutus-section text-center container">
    <h2 id="AboutUs">About Us</h2>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-8 col-lg-3">
        <img src="/images/Ben.png" alt="">
        <h3>Ben Pawlett</h3>
        <p><em>Founder and Director</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-10 col-lg-9 aboutus">
        <p>Established in 2016, Pawlett Plumbing & Heating Ltd are a local family-run business operating throughout Aberdeenshire and surrounding areas. We pride ourselves on offering our customers a high quality, friendly and reliable service.
As an approved member of the Gas Safe Organisation we aim to provide the highest standard of professional workmanship and expertise for all domestic and commercial plumbing and heating requirements with a 24-hour emergency call out service also in place.
If you have any Plumbing and Heating related requirements or queries, please don’t hesitate to get in contact with us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="testimonials-section container">
    <h2 class="text-center">What Our Customers Say</h2>
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-5">
        <blockquote class="blockquote px-5">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          <p class="mb-0">Fabulous service from this company. Will definitely be using and recommending them in future. Ben got straight back to me when I contacted him about an issue with our heating system. He arrived when he said he would, sorted the problem and was very thorough in checking everything was working as it should before he left.</p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer">Joanne Taylor <cite title="Source Title"></cite></footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5">
        <blockquote class="blockquote px-5">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          <p class="mb-0">Great to have met Ben and his colleague Chris who have worked so diligently this last week. I cannot praise them enough and can really recommend them in all ways- very polite , tidy , punctual and dependable.</p>
          <footer class="blockquote-footer">Hazel Bannerman<cite title="Source Title"></cite></footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/reviews" class="text-center d-block">See more customer testimonials</a>
  </div>
  <div class="contact-section">
    <%= render 'specialist/contact' %>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-section">
    <%= render 'shared/footer' %>
  </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>





